Author: DelicateFknFlower
Text: thank you for reaching out ❤️ I have wonderful people in my life for support. I’ve been keeping the eating and drinking a secret though, trying to muster up the strength to come clean. thank god for therapy I guess :’)

Author: sleepybear7
Text: I am so sorry you are going through this. Any one of those things could cause someone to relapse, never mind so many things in a single year. You deserve attention and sympathy! Do you have any supportive people in your life who can help you this? I hope your mom makes a full recovery and the rest of your year is better. ❤️
